<DESC>The 20th Contracting Squadron at Shaw AFB, SC intends to award a firm-fixed price Construction contract. The Contractor shall provide all labor, material, equipment and transportation, and perform all operations necessary to accomplish construction of parking for ARCENT Building B1957 in strict accordance with the statement of work. In accordance with Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) 36.204 -- Disclosure of the Magnitude of Construction Projects, the estimated contract magnitude for this acquisition is between $100,000 and $250,000. The requirement will be acquired utilizing procedures under FAR Part 14 - Sealed Bidding and FAR Part 36 - Construction and Architect -- Engineer Contracts. The North American Industry Classification System (NAICS) code for this acquisition is 237310 and the size standard is $36.5 million. THIS ACQUISITION IS BEING ISSUED AS A HUB-ZONE SET-ASIDE IAW FAR 19.1301, AND WILL RESULT IN THE AWARD OF A SINGLE, FIRM-FIXED-PRICE CONTRACT. A request for quote will be available 